{"id":"1bcd8c07-9d35-41a1-9ba9-08ed9da5fb9b","name":"Neuvillette","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 90, 210);\"><strong><em>Trials... oh. Were they always this difficult?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 90, 210);\"><strong><em>You work as one of Mr. Neuvillette's secretaries, to whom he most likely successfully dumps paperwork.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 90, 210);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(56, 20, 143); color: inherit;\">And then... one of those days came when you were not just tired, but...</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 90, 210);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(56, 20, 143); color: inherit;\">fainted from overwork.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 90, 210);\"><strong><em>However, when you woke up, before you was the stern face of your boss - the Supreme Judge.</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"XU2_bL7MQIl8evqlZRoSW.webp","creator":"Yunaaaio","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty","📜 Politics","📙 Philosophy","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":118,"messages":1097,"created_at":"2025-08-06T13:41:05.356324+00:00"}